So two weeks ago, I played Bubble Bobble on an old-fashioned Arcade Machine, needed coins and everything. And since then, I've had the main theme stuck in my head. I've also been listening to the whole list over the past week in an attempt to drive it out. Then today, finally, it stopped repeating.

So much for that. Ah well, at least it's nice.
